{"tid":780361,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：旺角牛布拉","createTime":"2018-08-15T06:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T13:10:40.000Z","uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f5101998aad6e8976a30f35ce7a485ac3d45d1d5","tid":780361,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:01:59.000Z","msg":"牛布拉呢個名，即刻令人諗起布拉腸粉，咁薄對我黎講就唔係賣點黎，但係見佢個 lunch set 又好似幾平幾多野食，就入去試下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個三色刺身飯其實真係唔錯，三舊刺身新鮮，濕潤，都算大舊，開胃。碗醋飯調味都有水準，食完就更開胃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/135819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F135819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fe8d5935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/135815_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F135815_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c5498b3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完飯先食返沙律同麵豉湯，冇跟次序嘅，呢兩樣就比較失色，沙律醬略嫌少，唔夠味。湯似乎亦都稀咗啲，冇麵豉應有嘅濃重口感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/135857_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F135857_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2762b547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係最後上碗麵就幾有水準喇，係佢嘅招牌牛布拉拌拉麵，有三塊薄牛肉，幾大塊嘅，雖然薄，但都食到豐富肉味啵。麵夠粗身，冇梘水味，咬落又夠彈牙，已經合格有突啦，佢仲有啲肉碎比你撈添。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/135918_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F135918_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=51893f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/135921_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F135921_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=acddb8b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有杯汽水送，夠多野食喇啩，咁究竟有幾平呢？88蚊加一，新張九折，即係都係88蚊。"},{"pid":"e27df2aa7f300c3d585cf0d846f7beda4db76729","tid":780361,"uid":130976,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"打手死開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8955ee7bd0a8c916c912d4aa690233aa637851","tid":780361,"uid":129221,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:36:20.000Z","msg":"三舊刺身新鮮，濕潤，都算大舊，開胃<br />\n樓豬係咪黎搞笑架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20dbe621c59c525e629673811afe751ed3521cb4","tid":780361,"uid":9395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"碗麵j m 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefda3147147571302569f2c0e1a7a682395bbec","tid":780361,"uid":92381,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛 咁都要$88？"},{"pid":"706cc4065c3d2304d4e16d98e3537797e7ebe7b8","tid":780361,"uid":60545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"d7aa326aa3b98c1296987dc591d3a79fd5ec2d74","tid":780361,"uid":87741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:40:23.000Z","msg":"打手味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe8e3d2d4626bfeab8a1f80368f521405a4e6fb","tid":780361,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:40:53.000Z","msg":"冇解釋白汁係咩"},{"pid":"53816ecc32ff8ca35ec9fa8bad0823eac6738455","tid":780361,"uid":31661,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":